2
00:00:30.572 --> 00:00:35.661
Hail Mary. full of grace. the Lord is with thee.

3
00:00:36.286 --> 00:00:39.540
Blessed art thou among women.

4
00:00:39.581 --> 00:00:42.000
and blessed is the fruit of thy womb Jesus.

5
00:00:43.585 --> 00:00:48.257
Holy Mary. Mother of God. pray for us sinners.

6
00:00:53.053 --> 00:00:55.389
Now and at the hour of our death.

7
00:04:10.292 --> 00:04:11.418
Help!

8
00:04:45.535 --> 00:04:47.496
Please...

9
00:04:49.331 --> 00:04:51.583
...help.

10
00:06:14.833 --> 00:06:16.459
What a waste.

11
00:06:17.127 --> 00:06:18.712
Look at her.

12
00:06:56.833 --> 00:06:58.251
Sister Cecilia.

13
00:06:58.668 --> 00:06:59.252
Apologies.

14
00:06:59.753 --> 00:07:01.963
I'm Deacon Enzo. Come with me.

15
00:07:37.248 --> 00:07:38.541
How much longer?

16
00:07:38.583 --> 00:07:39.960
We're almost there.

17
00:08:27.382 --> 00:08:29.300
Right this way. Sister Cecilia.

18
00:08:39.394 --> 00:08:40.812
Sister Cecilia!

19
00:08:44.357 --> 00:08:47.736
Your eyes radiate the light of the Holy Spirit.

20
00:08:48.278 --> 00:08:51.322
Like the angels delivered you
straight from the heavens.

21
00:08:51.740 --> 00:08:54.242
We've been eagerly awaiting your arrival.
my dear.

22
00:09:06.713 --> 00:09:09.340
Isabelle. will you please show Cecilia
to her room?

23
00:09:09.716 --> 00:09:12.594
I have to help our sisters get ready
for tonight's celebration.

24
00:09:12.635 --> 00:09:14.846
Mind your place and do as I ask!

25
00:09:47.587 --> 00:09:48.546
Hello. Sisters.

26
00:09:49.255 --> 00:09:51.007
This is our new novice. Sister Cecilia.

27
00:10:04.395 --> 00:10:06.147
Have you seen my daddy?

28
00:10:06.564 --> 00:10:10.193
Yes. let's go find him. shall we?

29
00:14:59.107 --> 00:15:04.404
In the name of the Father. the Son.
and the Holy Spirit.

30
00:20:44.910 --> 00:20:47.496
Sometimes we get caught up in emotion.

31
00:21:10.436 --> 00:21:13.272
Saint Helena. Mother of Constantine...

32
00:21:13.814 --> 00:21:15.524
...brought this back from Jerusalem.

33
00:21:16.734 --> 00:21:17.401
Here.

34
00:21:22.656 --> 00:21:24.658
He suffered on the cross.

35
00:21:41.550 --> 00:21:46.555
For you. For us. For our sins.
For our salvation.

36
00:21:49.683 --> 00:21:51.477
In the name of His love.

37
00:21:52.853 --> 00:21:53.938
It is a gift.

38
00:22:02.238 --> 00:22:03.656
Are you alright. Sister?

39
00:25:08.549 --> 00:25:12.428
Good morning. Sisters.
Today a new life begins.

40
00:25:13.345 --> 00:25:14.930
But this new year will not be easy.

41
00:25:15.723 --> 00:25:17.599
You will question your purpose.

42
00:25:17.641 --> 00:25:21.103
You will question me
and why you have come here.

43
00:25:21.770 --> 00:25:25.399
And some of you will not have
the spiritual fortitude for this life.

44
00:25:37.911 --> 00:25:39.955
Do you find this amusing. Sister Guendalina?

45
00:25:41.165 --> 00:25:42.499
No. forgive me.

46
00:25:42.541 --> 00:25:44.501
This side of the room is with me.

47
00:25:45.252 --> 00:25:49.173
The other. will serve with Sister Isabelle.

48
00:25:57.890 --> 00:25:59.808
Looks like her vibrator ran out of battery.

49
00:26:28.253 --> 00:26:31.465
First you have to make sure
your knife is nice and sharp.

50
00:26:31.507 --> 00:26:33.300
Otherwise you run the risk of making a big mess.

51
00:28:08.478 --> 00:28:10.230
Blessed.

52
00:28:11.190 --> 00:28:13.066
Saint.

53
00:28:13.901 --> 00:28:16.820
All of us adore you.

54
00:28:38.759 --> 00:28:41.762
Blessed Saint Cecilia.

55
00:31:23.757 --> 00:31:26.009
Sister Cecilia. Come with me.

56
00:32:00.627 --> 00:32:01.503
Your Eminence.

57
00:32:01.962 --> 00:32:02.921
Sit.

58
00:32:52.471 --> 00:32:54.431
Have you kept your vow of poverty?

59
00:32:56.850 --> 00:32:58.351
Have you remained chaste?

60
00:33:49.444 --> 00:33:51.821
When she arrived. Dr. Gallo.
did you examine her?

61
00:33:51.863 --> 00:33:53.198
Her hymen was intact.

62
00:33:53.573 --> 00:33:56.368
It's never been touched.

63
00:34:09.756 --> 00:34:12.926
Mother Superior. have we had
visitors during these last few weeks?

64
00:35:17.532 --> 00:35:19.200
This child was...

65
00:35:20.035 --> 00:35:22.287
...conceived without sin.

66
00:35:24.831 --> 00:35:26.207
As God as my witness...

67
00:35:28.418 --> 00:35:30.587
...we have been blessed with a miracle.

68
00:39:24.070 --> 00:39:27.448
It was supposed to be me! Bitch!

69
00:39:39.836 --> 00:39:40.920
Sisters!

70
00:39:40.962 --> 00:39:41.754
Stop it!

71
00:39:41.796 --> 00:39:42.881
Leave her alone!

72
00:39:43.631 --> 00:39:44.424
Stop!

73
00:39:46.926 --> 00:39:48.469
We have to try again!

74
00:39:48.511 --> 00:39:50.930
They have to try again with me!

75
00:39:51.306 --> 00:39:54.017
They have to try again with me!

76
00:41:48.131 --> 00:41:50.091
Bless you. young mother.

77
00:42:40.099 --> 00:42:41.309
All of you. go.

78
00:42:42.518 --> 00:42:43.978
Go away. I said!

79
00:43:36.697 --> 00:43:37.824
Don't touch me.

80
00:43:42.161 --> 00:43:45.081
How the fuck can you just stand there
as if nothing happened?

81
00:43:45.623 --> 00:43:47.792
Cecilia's pregnant and we don't know how.

82
00:43:47.834 --> 00:43:50.670
Isabelle killed herself.
What the fuck is going on?

83
00:43:50.711 --> 00:43:53.089
Let go of me!
I know when a man is lying to me.

84
00:43:53.464 --> 00:43:57.426
And all of you. every single one of you.
is so full of bullshit!

85
00:43:57.468 --> 00:43:59.303
Let go of me! Let go of me!

86
00:43:59.345 --> 00:44:00.346
Let go of me!

87
00:44:01.806 --> 00:44:03.766
Let go of me! I said let me go!

88
00:49:47.234 --> 00:49:49.987
Let me go! Let me go!

89
00:49:59.246 --> 00:50:01.957
No. I'm begging you. please.

90
00:50:44.291 --> 00:50:45.793
Blessed...

91
00:51:54.528 --> 00:51:55.487
What's happening?

92
00:51:55.529 --> 00:51:56.363
I don't know.

93
00:51:58.240 --> 00:52:00.075
Mother! What's going on?

94
00:52:00.117 --> 00:52:01.368
I don't know. father.

95
00:52:07.666 --> 00:52:08.459
God in Heaven.

96
00:52:10.919 --> 00:52:11.712
Call Doctor Gallo.

97
00:52:11.754 --> 00:52:12.963
It's not possible. it's Saturday.

98
00:52:13.005 --> 00:52:13.631
Call him!

99
00:52:13.672 --> 00:52:14.923
I won't get a hold of him. it's Saturday.

100
00:52:15.633 --> 00:52:16.634
We need to get her to the hospital.

101
00:52:16.675 --> 00:52:17.343
No.

102
00:52:17.384 --> 00:52:19.094
You must go. Now.

103
00:52:19.136 --> 00:52:19.637
No.

104
00:52:19.928 --> 00:52:21.180
That's it. I'm calling an ambulance.

105
00:52:21.221 --> 00:52:21.972
Stop!

106
00:52:57.216 --> 00:52:58.884
What do we do if she dies on the way there?

107
00:53:00.094 --> 00:53:01.553
We must maintain hope.

108
00:53:02.846 --> 00:53:03.806
It ain't looking good.

109
00:53:03.847 --> 00:53:04.807
Then we shall pray.

110
00:54:09.079 --> 00:54:09.538
Yes.

111
00:54:30.309 --> 00:54:31.018
I understand.

112
00:54:37.900 --> 00:54:38.692
Stop the car.

113
00:54:39.735 --> 00:54:40.235
What?

114
00:54:40.277 --> 00:54:41.195
Stop the car.

115
00:55:49.388 --> 00:55:50.430
Now you're ashamed?

116
00:55:51.014 --> 00:55:51.473
Now?

117
00:55:52.182 --> 00:55:56.311
Where was your shame when you
stuffed a dead animal inside yourself?

118
00:55:59.690 --> 00:56:00.649
Shame on you.

119
00:56:01.108 --> 00:56:03.485
Making us believe the miracle died inside you.

120
00:56:04.820 --> 00:56:06.029
What do you have to say for yourself?

121
